summary: The document is an Indenture dated October 21, 2025, among Exeter Automobile Receivables Trust 2025-5 (Issuer), Exeter Holdings Trust 2025-5 (Holding Trust), and Citibank, N.A. (Indenture Trustee), outlining the terms for various classes of asset-backed notes. It details the responsibilities, rights, and obligations of the parties involved, including the payment of principal and interest, covenants, and remedies in case of default. The Indenture also specifies the roles and duties of the Indenture Trustee and the procedures for noteholder communications and supplemental indentures.
